{"tid":1771650,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"維基百科『百無一用是書生』除咗係五毛，仲係香港文化嘅謀殺者","createTime":"2019-12-06T04:27:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T12:06:03.000Z","uid":89937,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ad16c2540f8de7aa174f4eae5efffc77e69d4840","tid":1771650,"uid":89937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T04:27:43.000Z","msg":"//近年已經有不少香港／華語音樂條目，被AT和百無一用是書生兩個管理員大量刪除。在台灣歌手袁詠琳初出道之時，百無一用是書生更曾經想刪去她的條目。他們的理據往往是沒有可靠來源，關注度不足。但不少要找資料來源其實不難（完全合乎要求去證明知名度就稍為困難），以他們的經驗，稍加資料來源只是舉手之勞。但他們卻選擇於不會為任何人帶來好處，保留只會有利無害的情況下刪去。（按現行機制，雖然要經動議程序和時間，但以往這些條目被動議刪去時，往往沒有人理會，最終就任由這些管理員刪去）<br />\n<br />\n上述的專輯，也許沒有大賣，也許不是這些藝人最傑出的作品，但他們絕對是香港流行音樂歷史的一部分。假如繼續讓他們主觀地刪去，可能我們的流行音樂就慢慢在歷史中消失。不論兩名管理員的動機是什麼，我們都只能把他們當作香港樂迷的敵人看待。<br />\n<br />\n也許還有其他地方會找到，但我相信無人希望，到頭來香港流行音樂的資料，要在中國大陸的百度百科才能找到。<br />\n<br />\n我希望大家能夠幫忙，去維基百科註冊戶口，盡可能去還未被刪去的香港／華語音樂條目，增加不同可靠的資料來源（可以是KKBox，YesAsia，Spotify等），抗衡這些香港樂迷的敵人。//<br />\n<br />\n張List唔Post過嚟，但關心妍同許廷鏗嘅碟都差唔多俾呢班仆街刪晒。真係要大家多啲去維基百科抗衡班五毛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cmusichart.com/discuz/viewthread.php?tid=16769&amp;extra=page%3D1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmusichart.com%2Fdiscuz%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D16769%26extra%3Dpage%253D1&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=a324c619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cmusichart.com/discuz/viewthread.php?tid=16769&amp;extra=page%3D1</a>"},{"pid":"92e947962fff5f42cee0c24ce8b7ddc7a4572477","tid":1771650,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T04:38:35.000Z","msg":"佢地唔用同一把「尺」去度先係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198ceeca76c81d2da5183fc46e72583f682670bd","tid":1771650,"uid":71237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"92e947962fff5f42cee0c24ce8b7ddc7a4572477","tid":1771650,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T04:38:35.000Z","msg":"佢地唔用同一把「尺」去度先係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T04:42:46.000Z","msg":"把尺喺度<br />\n維基百科:關注度<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:%E5%85%B3%E6%B3%A8%E5%BA%A6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FWikipedia%3A%25E5%2585%25B3%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E5%25BA%25A6&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=a1c2d32e\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:%E5%85%B3%E6%B3%A8%E5%BA%A6</a><br />\n維基百科:關注度 (音樂)<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E5%BA%A6_(%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FWikipedia%3A%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E5%25BA%25A6_%28%25E9%259F%25B3%25E6%25A8%2582%29&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=3e315c03\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E5%BA%A6_(%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82)</a><br />\n<br />\n如果唱片條目符合到依把尺，就唔會被刪除。"},{"pid":"ba2a3e0219434b2fe1b02573bf26b499d8644046","tid":1771650,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T04:44:11.000Z","msg":"樓主你叫人去搵KKBox、Spotify做sources明顯無用。<br />\n<br />\n你應該叫人去圖書館搵下啲講香港音樂嘅書，入面有介紹到依啲唱片就可以證明有關注度。"},{"pid":"4440d3385cc44d620db81cb1fcc5de53442a65cc","tid":1771650,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T04:47:59.000Z","msg":"人地刪除香港音樂專輯，係因為證明唔到關注度。<br />\n你唔可以自己唔搵資料來源，然後怪刪除者唔幫你搵，並指控刪除者係五毛。<br />\n<br />\n號召更多人參與維基百科係好事，但係誤導大家以為加Spotify、KKBox做參考來源就得，對成件事係無幫助。"},{"pid":"2abffdc7d31574f23e3d381ae342355d9dfe2cb5","tid":1771650,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T04:50:04.000Z","msg":"另一個可行方向就係修改維基百科嘅方針，你可以去互助客棧提出放寬音樂專輯的關注度要求。"},{"pid":"19607f1bd5b8e4d1f7365ad9e8d68ae7e89e67e9","tid":1771650,"uid":89937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba2a3e0219434b2fe1b02573bf26b499d8644046","tid":1771650,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T04:44:11.000Z","msg":"樓主你叫人去搵KKBox、Spotify做sources明顯無用。<br />\n<br />\n你應該叫人去圖書館搵下啲講香港音樂嘅書，入面有介紹到依啲唱片就可以證明有關注度。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T09:11:13.000Z","msg":"咁你覺得有乜source?<br />\n我同意呢幾個唔夠，但好過無。"},{"pid":"3fa7a545b844661ffcef454df982a0b560744a70","tid":1771650,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"19607f1bd5b8e4d1f7365ad9e8d68ae7e89e67e9","tid":1771650,"uid":89937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba2a3e0219434b2fe1b02573bf26b499d8644046","tid":1771650,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T04:44:11.000Z","msg":"樓主你叫人去搵KKBox、Spotify做sources明顯無用。<br />\n<br />\n你應該叫人去圖書館搵下啲講香港音樂嘅書，入面有介紹到依啲唱片就可以證明有關注度。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T09:11:13.000Z","msg":"咁你覺得有乜source?<br />\n我同意呢幾個唔夠，但好過無。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T09:26:39.000Z","msg":"我無信心救到每張唱片嘅條目，最理想完美的做法應該係搵下有冇唱片銷量、有冇書籍、雜誌介紹香港流行音樂。<br />\n可能需要去公共圖書館或者大學圖書館搵下資料。<br />\n<br />\n我Google Book搵咗一堆書，唔一定對近期被刪有幫助，但入面如果提到某些歌曲、歌手、專輯，都可以引用。我知咁樣好麻煩，但理想做法就係咁。<br />\n<br />\n詞中物：香港流行歌詞探賞<br />\n<a href=\"https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=Ne6qAAAAQBAJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com.hk%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DNe6qAAAAQBAJ&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=a08217a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=Ne6qAAAAQBAJ</a><br />\n<br />\n歲月如歌－－詞話香港粵語流行曲<br />\n<a href=\"https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=rfOqAAAAQBAJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com.hk%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DrfOqAAAAQBAJ&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=a50accf1\" target=\"_blank\">https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=rfOqAAAAQBAJ</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭國江詞畫人生(第二版) <br />\n<a href=\"https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=uj3NBAAAQBAJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com.hk%2Fbooks%3Fid%3Duj3NBAAAQBAJ&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=30ae6a63\" target=\"_blank\">https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=uj3NBAAAQBAJ</a><br />\n<br />\n香港詞人系列：盧國沾<br />\n<a href=\"https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=qr_sDQAAQBAJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com.hk%2Fbooks%3Fid%3Dqr_sDQAAQBAJ&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=1d5127c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=qr_sDQAAQBAJ</a><br />\n<br />\n盧國沾詞評選<br />\n<a href=\"https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=M4FYCgAAQBAJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com.hk%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DM4FYCgAAQBAJ&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=73276eae\" target=\"_blank\">https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=M4FYCgAAQBAJ</a><br />\n<br />\n原創先鋒: 粵曲人的流行曲調創作<br />\n<a href=\"https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=8HTNBAAAQBAJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com.hk%2Fbooks%3Fid%3D8HTNBAAAQBAJ&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=baa63786\" target=\"_blank\">https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=8HTNBAAAQBAJ</a><br />\n<br />\n香港詞人系列：鄭國江<br />\n<a href=\"https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=sOynDgAAQBAJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com.hk%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DsOynDgAAQBAJ&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=a1a3fbae\" target=\"_blank\">https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=sOynDgAAQBAJ</a><br />\n<br />\n香港詞人系列：黃霑<br />\n<a href=\"https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=HOynDgAAQBAJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com.hk%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DHOynDgAAQBAJ&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=e8eb750e\" target=\"_blank\">https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=HOynDgAAQBAJ</a><br />\n<br />\n香港流行歌詞研究: 70年代中期至90年代中期<br />\n<a href=\"https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=v74pAQAAIAAJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com.hk%2Fbooks%3Fid%3Dv74pAQAAIAAJ&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=83b6913e\" target=\"_blank\